headline.main: Yemen Security Officials Say Al-Qaida Kills 11 Soldiers
headline.print_headline: Yemen Security Officials Say Al-Qaida Kills 11 Soldiers

lead_paragraph: Yemeni security officials say that al-Qaida militants have killed 11 soldiers in two separate attacks.
